{"tid":545594,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"打飛機畀roommate睇到","createTime":"2018-01-30T16:06:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-31T15:52:31.000Z","uid":42927,"like":5,"dislike":58,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"9e707b6d6a4efc40c255614f84d17e94bce09449","tid":545594,"uid":42927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T16:06:15.000Z","msg":"琴晚見roommate唔返宿舍，間房冇人所以喺房鎖好門開咗套AV睇，睇睇下仲除咗衫褲開始打。<br />\n<br />\n完事後我除低咗耳機同用紙巾抹身，正當我拎啲紙巾去掉嗰陣，拎轉頭一望居然見到我roommate企咗喺門口度。<br />\n<br />\n可能因為我戴咗耳聲又開得大聲，所以全程都唔覺佢入咗房。見到佢之後，全裸嘅我成個人呆咗唔知點反應。<br />\n<br />\n佢就笑住問咗我一句：「你做咩喺房唔著衫？」我情急之下就同佢講我啱啱倒瀉嘢喺身所以除咗衫褲嚟抹。<br />\n<br />\n然後佢繼續笑住同我講：「咁你下次小心啲啦」，跟住就走咗去沖涼了。 <br />\n<br />\n我唔知佢有冇睇到啲咩，唔知佢會點諗。呢件事之後我連同佢講嘢都好似有啲尷尬咁，可以點做？佢會唔會好介意見到啲咁嘅嘢？"},{"pid":"7eb6204c25786f1ab63e0087226a7392d88042c0","tid":545594,"uid":11506,"like":97,"dislike":3,"score":94,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T16:13:27.000Z","msg":"打咪打囉屌 尷乜尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你rm日日係hall打你唔知咋"},{"pid":"305c8538300a213757d24d64bb49e7f90812552b","tid":545594,"uid":35946,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T16:15:26.000Z","msg":"你鎖咗門佢點入嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f401f3bb4d01b6d21289afcf9cd936e00f2d9469","tid":545594,"uid":61903,"like":144,"dislike":1,"score":143,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T16:21:32.000Z","msg":"其實佢全程望住你打飛機個樣黎打飛機"},{"pid":"ac223299cdba1c4fb50fd333b0b93e848efbb0e6","tid":545594,"uid":70808,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T16:21:54.000Z","msg":"GAY<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28893ae1695232e06f723fcd3dbb11178429c4af","tid":545594,"uid":42927,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"7eb6204c25786f1ab63e0087226a7392d88042c0","tid":545594,"uid":11506,"like":97,"dislike":3,"score":94,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T16:13:27.000Z","msg":"打咪打囉屌 尷乜尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\